Sady Rebbot https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sady_Rebbot 0 Sady Rebbot (27 April 1935 – 12 October 1994) was a French actor. He appeared in 68 films and television shows between 1959 and 1994. He starred alongside Anna Karina in the 1962 film Vivre sa vie. Sady_Rebbot ( 27_April_1935 – 12_October_1994 ) was a_French_actor .
